712754f-b.title: Manhattan: 41st Street - Dyer Avenue
712754f-b.text:
West 41st Street, west from Dyer Avenue, the new thorough-
fare that leads to the Lincoln Tunnel. This is between
Ninth and Tenth Avenue's. The photographer is viewing
towards the latter and beyond which appears the spire atop
St. Raphaels R. C. Church. View 2 is limited to the north
side of the street, detailing the structures lying between
Dyer and Tenth Avenue's.
September 4, 1940
No's. 1-2
P. L. Sperr
NO REIRODUCTIOhS
